T1  - Antecedents and Consequences of Research Planning in a University Setting
AU  - Glueck, William F.
AU  - Deich, Ingrid
Y1  - 1973/10/01
PY  - 1973
DA  - 1973/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.20.2.240
